    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Out Now!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/5808ea2b6c80544a0fad422a771eeeee.poster.avif?t=1762039282\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/5808ea2b6c80544a0fad422a771eeeee.webm?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/5808ea2b6c80544a0fad422a771eeeee.mp4?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ARM OF SATAN is a tough 2D platformer designed for unique </strong><strong><i>2-player co-op</i></strong><strong>.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring <strong>kick ass visuals</strong> influenced by the <i>Hellboy</i> comics, <strong>arcade-inspired</strong> gameplay, and a <strong>deep</strong> and <strong>captivating narrative</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game can be played single-player as a <i>difficult twin-stick</i>, but it is designed to be a <i>truly awesome</i> <strong>co-op experience</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/5fbcfb6d07d085b6a669f13073a7518b.poster.avif?t=1762039282\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/5fbcfb6d07d085b6a669f13073a7518b.webm?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/5fbcfb6d07d085b6a669f13073a7518b.mp4?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm of Satan follows the journey of two characters: <strong>Girl &amp; Arm</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Girl </strong>should not be here. <strong>Arm</strong> claims to know a way out…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Together, they descend through the underworlds in search of <i>salvation</i>… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GIRL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/f8131c1e929dff0036ced9ebd1d8e3f6.poster.avif?t=1762039282\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/f8131c1e929dff0036ced9ebd1d8e3f6.webm?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/f8131c1e929dff0036ced9ebd1d8e3f6.mp4?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Girl controls like a classic platformer. She is in charge of movement and jumping.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(great for onboarding newer or younger players). </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/9c1502cbd2d09267486d9b9b7e575d00.poster.avif?t=1762039282\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/9c1502cbd2d09267486d9b9b7e575d00.webm?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/9c1502cbd2d09267486d9b9b7e575d00.mp4?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arm is an action-oriented role: grabbing, punching and throwing  to protect Girl.</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TOGETHER...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/acdffb5efb80a23af3ef33e777014e0b.poster.avif?t=1762039282\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/acdffb5efb80a23af3ef33e777014e0b.webm?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/acdffb5efb80a23af3ef33e777014e0b.mp4?t=1762039282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Girl &amp; Arm must synchronise to traverse, dodge and climb their way through the treacherous depths of the underworld.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARCADE MODE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Finished the story? Play endlessly in ARCADE MODE, the dedicated speed-running mode with 'Tribulations' that challenge you to set fast times.</strong></p>",
